WHAT THIS PROJECT USES

A subset of KanjiVG stroke paths covering the 46 base hiragana taught in
Lingua's Japanese Unit 1 track. Paths are stored verbatim in KanjiVG's native
109x109 SVG coordinate space. No modifications to the path geometry were made;
only the subset selection differs from the full KanjiVG dataset.
